name: Health X Change
description: Health X Change aims to get people paid for their health data while pushing medicine forward. We are a novel platform that incentivizes patients to share their health data by providing tokens as compensation. We also offer privacy preserving AI tools to maange health and insurance directly to our patients. As Health X Change strikes commercial and R&D partnerships with pharma companies, a portion of generated revenues will be used to provide value back to our tokenholders. We also have ambitions to create novel drugs and devices by leveraging user generated data, always passing back a portion to our tokenholders. Join our Discord and follow us on Twitter today!
